Notes:

To access git bash on a project, simply right click the main folder of project then select git bash

to create a file using git bash "touch index.html"

to initialize the git on your project "git init" - this will create .git folder but by default, you can not see it because it is hidden.

BEFORE START ADD NAME AND EMAIL TO GIT
git config --global user.name 'Gab Adawag'
git config --global user.email 'me@gadawag.com'

TO ADD A FILE TO GIT REPOSITORY
git add index.html //add specific file
git add *.html //add all html file
git add . //will add all files


TO SEE WHAT IS IN THE STAGING AREA
git status
